<item>
            <title>[DERBY-5083] Document automatic update and creation of index cardinality statistics (istat)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-5083</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Documentation is needed for the automatic index statistics feature (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4934&quot; title=&quot;Provide automatic update and creation of index cardinality statistics (istat)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-4934&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-4934&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). It appears that a change is needed to the Tuning Guide topic &quot;When cardinality statistics are automatically updated&quot;, at least.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
